# YAP â€” Project Overview

**YAP** ("Your Campus, Unfiltered") is an anonymous campus social + marketplace app for **University of Exeter** students. Verified via `@exeter.ac.uk` email. Gen Z, minimalist, Apple-inspired UI with Exeter green accent.

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js 16** (App Router, Turbopack dev) + **React 19** + **TypeScript**
- **Tailwind CSS v4** (`@import "tailwindcss"` in `globals.css`, `@theme inline` for tokens)
- **Auth.js (NextAuth v5)** + **Prisma** (SQLite) + **Resend** magic-link email auth
- **Zustand** â€” app state (`src/lib/store.ts`); auth sessions via NextAuth
- **Framer Motion** â€” page transitions, landing animations
- **Leaflet / react-leaflet** â€” Nightlife map (SSR disabled via `dynamic()`)
- **Stripe** â€” ticket checkout + Connect Express seller onboarding
- **Lucide React** â€” icons (`src/lib/icons.ts` for custom mappings)

## App Structure

Single-page app: `src/app/page.tsx` orchestrates everything after auth.

| Route / Tab | Component | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Unauthenticated | `HeroSection` | Landing + `@exeter.ac.uk` email verification flow |
| `feed` | `FeedPage` | Anonymous posts, reactions, polls, comments |
| `market` | `MarketplacePage` | Student marketplace (textbooks, electronics, etc.) |
| `nightlife` | `NightlifePage` | Ticket resale + Exeter nightlife map |
| `profile` | `ProfilePage` | User karma, stats |
| Overlay | `SettingsPage`, `NotificationsPage` | Full-screen overlays via store flags |

Navigation: `BottomNav` (5 tabs: Feed, Market, Night, Post, Profile). Create opens `CreatePostModal`.

## State Management

All app state in `useStore` (`src/lib/store.ts`). **Auth** via NextAuth session (`useSession`, `auth()`). Mock data in `src/lib/mock-data.ts`. Theme persisted to `localStorage` (`theme-preference`).

Key store domains: auth, feed (posts/reactions/polls), comments, marketplace (listings/saved), nightlife (tickets/pins), conversations/messages, notifications, UI (tabs/modals/search), settings.

## Types

Defined in `src/types/index.ts`: `Post`, `Listing`, `Comment`, `NightlifeTicket`, `NightlifePin`, `Notification`, `Conversation`, etc.

Post categories: `confessions | hot-takes | questions | memes | events | rants | advice`
Reactions: `fire | cap | dead | real | sus` (Gen Z slang, not likes)
Market categories: `textbooks | electronics | furniture | clothing | bikes | tickets | other`

## Design System

- **Brand color**: Exeter green `#00796B` (`--color-exeter`, `bg-exeter` Tailwind class)
- **Font**: Geist Sans (layout), design-system.md references Fredoka but code uses Geist
- **Dark mode**: `.dark` class on root, CSS variables in `globals.css`
- **Mobile-first**: `max-w-2xl` content, bottom nav, `min-h-dvh`, safe-area insets
- **Landing**: dark video hero (`/exeter-campus.mp4`), glass buttons

## API Routes

- `GET/POST /api/auth/[...nextauth]` â€” Auth.js handlers (magic link sign-in)
- `POST /api/stripe/checkout` â€” Stripe Checkout for nightlife tickets (auth required)
- `POST /api/stripe/connect/onboard` â€” Stripe Connect Express onboarding (auth required)
- Env: `AUTH_SECRET`, `AUTH_URL`, `DATABASE_URL`, `AUTH_RESEND_KEY`, `EMAIL_FROM`, `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`

## File Layout

```
