- Client components use `'use client'`
- Path alias: `@/` â†’ `src/`
- New posts/listings generate IDs with `Date.now()` prefix
- Nightlife map pins: `nightclub` (green) vs `house-party` (amber)
- No tests, no CI config, no database â€” prototype/MVP stage
